                <note rend="inline" type="source">817.00/2868: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Minister in Nicaragua</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Ramer</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1922-05-23T18:00:00-04:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">May 23, 1922—6 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>21. Your 31, May 21, 11 p.m.</p>
                <p>Your action is approved and the Department desires to commend the prompt and
                    capable manner in which you handled the situation.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hughes</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
